author: Outdoor Boys
description:
For 3 yeas I have wanted to find a set of walrus tusks and this time its finally happening. I am flying to a remote part of western Alaska on the shores of the Bering Sea where I will be camping alone in bear country, hiking, beach combing, searching for shed caribou antlers and hunting for dead walrus ivory.
